author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Shower water supply line protection tips…I use a 5x8 safety plate and 3-inch or 5-inch self-nailing stud guards for any pipe or electrical penetrations. Also, I take pictures of the wall for reference so I can avoid the plates while installing shower backer boards.
